<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BLACKGHOST</title>
    <style>
        /* Estilos gerais */
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), 
                        url('https://media3.giphy.com/media/4fCFRodZ5tJu0/giphy.gif?cid=6c09b952fnrajb7idqisg7ilhuff02fa1irkdr54d23mwe8k&ep=v1_internal_gif_by_id&rid=giphy.gif&ct=g') 
                        no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
            color: white;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        h1, p, nav a, footer {
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); /* Sombra para o texto */
        }
        /* Botão de estilo */
        .button-2 {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border: 2px solid #ffffff;
            border-radius: 25px;
            background-color: transparent;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .button-2:hover {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: black;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #808080;
        }
        .scroll-log {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #00ff00;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .scroll-log p {
            animation: scroll 5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
            margin: 0;
        }
        @keyframes scroll {
            0% { transform: translateX(100%); }
            50% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
            100% { transform: translateX(100%); }
        }
        /* Menu de navegação */
        nav {
            background-color: #000;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 10;
            text-align: left;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .nav-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center; /* Alinha os links ao centro */
            width: auto;
        }
        nav a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #00ff00;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .nav-container {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #00ff00;
            width: auto;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Menu de navegação -->
    <nav>
    <div class="nav-container">
        <a href="index.html">Home</a>
        <a href="contato.html">Contato</a>
    </div>
</nav>
    
    <h1>@BLACKGHOST_B</h1>
    <p>Estamos em desenvolvimento, aguarde novidades!</p>
    
      
    <!-- Scrollslog -->
    <div class="scroll-log">
        <p>Em breve mais atualizações para os nossos usuários!</p>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        Todos os direitos reservados a @BLACKGHOST_B | 2024/2025
    </footer>
</body>
</html>